content:
Yaka dhuwala museum — dhuwala djäl-ŋupanamirri.
Dhuwala dhäruk'dhäruk yaka balaŋu walala marrtjinya— ŋanydja djäma bili.

*******

Dhuwala wäŋa internetŋura dhäwumirri ga milŋ'thun.

*******

Ŋanapurru ga ḻapthun dhuwalawa dhärukju ḏurryunawa.

Gupapuyŋu gäthura.
Gàidhlig galki.
Yurruna yolŋu dhärukmirri.
